{"tid":2077761,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［FF討論］當世界沒有了利益","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T18:02:08.000Z","uid":339084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe029bec0e04aee82594f90c5ed453734b19292","tid":2077761,"uid":339084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"「阻鬼住曬！快啲立法拉曬啲暴徒！我要做生意架」<br />\n「支持立法！還我經濟」<br />\n「再唔立法，個個星期咁樣真係租都唔使交」<br />\n<br />\n政權只不過是看準了人貪婪的性格而加以利用，<br />\n當我們身處的世界失去利益，<br />\n人們不再計較利益<br />\n又會是一個怎麼的世界？"},{"pid":"e8e8e76ad60854e536147dccb14e6f7e21b5487b","tid":2077761,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"求核戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d45d95f53309617e844f0696ae6d4942beaade","tid":2077761,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T18:02:08.000Z","msg":"虛擬世界<br />\n任何政治都係為利益"}]}